# ACTIVE CODEBASE CONTEXT

## This is the ONLY working codebase:

**`kimi-ide-client/`** - React + TypeScript + Vite client (ACTIVE)

The server (`kimi-ide-server/`) only exists to:
1. Serve the built React client from `kimi-ide-client/dist/`
2. Handle WebSocket connections to the Kimi wire process
3. Route JSON-RPC messages

